metadata.name: You’re a Square
metadata.description:
You’re a square who makes a square, who makes a square, who makes a square…
and that’s how structure works.
 
What is a limitation of a Human Structure? We can produce only what we know. We grow and explore but to a limit of what we perceive. We think in binaries , We read from left to right, We walk in lines and our entire reality comes from a screen. 

(Wait for the entire animation)
